Cluster balancer commands

Usage:
  grainfs cluster balancer [command]

Available Commands:
  status      Show cluster balancer state and per-node load stats

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for balancer

Global Flags:
      --endpoint string    admin Unix socket path (required, e.g. ./tmp/admin.sock)
      --format string      Output format: text or json (status/peers/events; ignored elsewhere) (default "text")
      --log-level string   log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")

Use "grainfs cluster balancer [command] --help" for more information about a command.
